# Icons

- Use **Hugeicons** for all icons in the app.
- Import the component from `@hugeicons/react-native` and icons from `@hugeicons/core-free-icons`.
- Do NOT use `@expo/vector-icons` (Ionicons, Feather, etc.).
- The only exception is SF Symbols (`Icon sf="..."`) inside `NativeTabs` in `app/(tabs)/_layout.tsx`.

## Usage

```tsx
import { HugeiconsIcon } from '@hugeicons/react-native';
import { Search01Icon } from '@hugeicons/core-free-icons';

<HugeiconsIcon icon={Search01Icon} size={24} color="#fff" />
```
